Un véritable animateur radio.

1169
01:48:22,320 --> 01:48:23,880
Merci, M.Wood.

1170
01:48:27,000 --> 01:48:29,120
Félicitations, votre Majesté.

1171
01:48:30,040 --> 01:48:32,840
